    participant KCluster as Konflux Cluster<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Dev,OLM: Flow 1: Operator Bundle Build (Konflux)
    Dev->>GH: Push to rhoai-2.19 branch
    GH->>Konflux: Webhook trigger<br/>TLS 1.2+ / GitHub App
    Konflux->>Quay: Push odh-operator-bundle<br/>HTTPS/443 / Registry Token
    alt Build Failure
        Konflux->>Slack: Failure notification<br/>HTTPS/443 / Webhook Secret
    end

    Note over Dev,OLM: Flow 2: FBC Fragment Build (Konflux)
    Konflux->>Konflux: Bundle build nudge
    Konflux->>Quay: Push rhoai-fbc-fragment<br/>HTTPS/443 / Registry Token

    Note over Dev,OLM: Flow 3: Bundle Processing (GitHub Actions)
    Dev->>GH: Push bundle-patch.yaml / csv-patch.yaml
    GH->>GHA: Webhook trigger<br/>TLS 1.2+ / GitHub Token
    GHA->>GH: Fetch RHOAI-Konflux-Automation utils<br/>HTTPS/443 / GitHub Token
    GHA->>KCluster: OC login<br/>HTTPS/443 / OC Token
    GHA->>Quay: Query image metadata<br/>HTTPS/443 / Quay API Token
    GHA->>GH: Commit processed bundle

    Note over Dev,OLM: Flow 4: Operator Deployment (Runtime)
    OLM->>Quay: Pull bundle + FBC images<br/>HTTPS/443 / Registry Creds
    OLM->>OLM: Install rhods-operator
    OLM->>EC: Verify supply chain policy
    EC-->>OLM: Policy result
